extendedInfo.description: The best Volleyball Training App for Android Phones and Tablets.  This cool and easy to use FLASH animated tutorial is designed to help Volleyball enthusiasts of all ages increase their Volleyball IQ while learning the fundamentals of playing Volleyball.It's a great, low-cost learning tool for aspiring high school, club and recreational Volleyball players.Each screen of the Volleyball Club Secrets Android App is divided into 7 areas. The top of each App screen displays animated examples. The bottom of each screen contains buttons that allow you to:View animated examples of Volleyball Serving Targets (by Target Number on the court)View Volleyball Net Zones (shows Zones of the Volleyball Net area)View animated examples of Volleyball Hitting Options (displays each hitting location on the Volleyball CourtView animated examples of Volleyball Setting Spots (Typical locations on the Volleyball Court used as targets by a Volleyball Setter)View animated examples of all 6 Volleyball Player Rotations in typical 5:1 and 6:2 formations, the two most common in Volleyball today.In addition, we provide an animated example of the 3 step Volleyball hitting approach.Club volleyball players spend years and thousands of dollars to obtain this information.  Club Volleyball Gear makes it available to anyone who has a passion for the game of Volleyball.
